range of industrial firms.  Professor Sabri Cetin , the board’s faculty coordinator, works with Department Head Farzad Mashayek to facilitate the board’s role in shaping the way in which UIC educates future mechanical and industrial engineers. In general, board members offer insight from industry that enhances the undergraduate program, and they provide points of connection between students and faculty and the professional engineering community.       photo block             Industry Members    Said Al-Hallaj, PhD , Co-Founder and Chairman/CEO, AllCell Technologies  Peyman Davoudabadi, PhD , Principal Engineer, ANSYS  Christina Martini , Partner, McDermott, Will, & Emery  Brad Mueller , Executive Vice President, Briggs Corporation  Majid Naghshineh, PhD , Director of Engineering, Hubbell Lighting Components  Melinda A. Riddick , MWL Engineering Manager, Caterpillar Inc.  Rudi Schick , Chief Science Officer, Spraying Systems Co.  David Smith, PhD , Associate Professor, College of DuPage  Michel Thenin , Spraying Systems Co.           About    Back to main content           Mechanical Engineering    Industrial Engineering    Energy Engineering    Advisory Board    Contact    Head's Message                   UIC Logo         College Of  Engineering           Quicklinks    Faculty Resources    Graduate Resources    Undergraduate Resources    ABET Accreditation    Contact UIC MIE         Contact   Department of Mechanical and Industrial Engineering  2039 Engineering Research Facility, 842 W. Taylor St., Chicago, IL 60607  Phone: (312) 996-5317  Fax: (312) 413-0447  mie@uic.edu        Social Media Accounts    Facebook    LinkedIn    Twitter    Instagram             UIC.edu links   UIC.edu  Academic Calendar  Athletics  Campus Directory  Disability Resources  Emergency Information  Event Calendar  Job Openings  Library  Maps  UIC Safe Mobile App  UIC Today  UI Health  Veterans Affairs        Powered by Red 2.38.0  © 2020 The Board of Trustees of the University of Illinois 